{"product_id":"nurme-neroli-gentle-facial-cleansing-foam-150ml","title":"NURME Neroli Gentle Facial Cleansing Foam 150ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis gentle face cleansing foam with neroli and passion fruit vitamins removes makeup and impurities. Pro-vitamin B5 and babassu oil enhance the skin’s moisture balance, leaving a flawless appearance without drying the skin. Suitable for all skin types.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe included pro-vitamin B5 and babassu oil boost and tone the skin’s moisture barrier for a radiant complexion. For the best results, follow up with a creamy cleanser to thoroughly remove daily dirt and prepare your skin for toning and deep hydration.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNeroli oil, derived from bitter orange blossoms, has powerful antimicrobial and antibacterial properties, making it ideal for acne-prone skin. It regulates sebum production, balancing oily skin. High in antioxidants and vitamin E, neroli oil combats free radicals, reducing acne inflammation and redness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to damp skin, gently massage and rinse clean.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Flower Water*, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate**, Citrus Aurantium Amara Flower Water*, Glycerin**, Panthenol*, Sodium Benzoate**, Potassium Sorbate**, Lactic Acid**, Benzyl Alcohol**, Passiflora Incarnata Extract*, Sodium Hyaluronate**.\n\u003cp\u003e* Natural origin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e** Natural cosmetics approved ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915891380551,"sku":null,"price":12.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-neroli-gentle-facial-cleansing-foam-150ml-259701.jpg?v=1739897181","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/nurme-neroli-gentle-facial-cleansing-foam-150ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}